  ('policepromo-8b7f1efc-moex-00035', 'policepromo-8b7f1efc', 'policepromo-8b7f1efc-moex-113-3082b5f1', 'sub-policepromo-8b7f1efc-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關損失補償責任之敘述，何者正確？', '["依警察職權行使法規定，人民有可歸責之事由時，不予補償", "依行政執行法規定，有可歸責於該人民之事由者，法院得減免補償金額", "依警械使用條例規定，有可歸責該第三人之事由時，得減輕或免除補償金額", "依行政程序法規定，廢止授予利益之合法行政處分，對受益人因信賴該處分致遭受財產上之損失，均不 予補償"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5cbcf5a16ce", "answer_pdf_sha1": "679249538eb6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "101", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "行政警察人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-8b7f1efc-moex-00036', 'policepromo-8b7f1efc', 'policepromo-8b7f1efc-moex-113-3082b5f1', 'sub-policepromo-8b7f1efc-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '受理訴願機關不得為下列何種決定？', '["不受理", "在訴願人表示不服之範圍內，逕為加重處罰之變更", "發回原行政處分機關另為處分", "針對課予義務訴願，指定相當期間，命應作為之機關速為一定之處分"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5cbcf5a16ce", "answer_pdf_sha1": "679249538eb6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "101", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "行政警察人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
